  <description><![CDATA[<p>A delightful hotel overlooking the Piazzetto in Porto Cervo, this is a unique location as it allows you to enjoy the tranquillity of the hotel but also a short walk brings you into the vibrant heart of Porto Cervo. The private beach of Li Nabani is accessed using the hotels shuttle service, located in an exclusive bay it’s a great place to spend the day relaxing.</p>
<p>The hotel has a central patio which is a great place to enjoy an early evening drink, before heading to either the Pescatore Restaurant serving amazing seafood with views across the bay of Porto Cervo or Restaurant Pergola specialising in traditional Mediterranean dishes with views across the harbour.</p>]]></description>
